{
  "texts": [
    "The FEVER (Thorne et al., 2018) dataset is mainly used for fact extraction and validation.",
    "Several RALM researchers, including Lewis et al. (2020), Wang et al. (2023c), and Izacard et al. (2022), have used the factual text in this dataset as a source of data.",
    "In addition to unstructured text, there is also a significant amount of inherently less structured data, such as images, videos, and audio.",
    "Several common image datasets are available for use in research, including MNIST, CIFAR-10, Pascal VOC, and COCO.",
    "Many studies (Chen et al., 2022b) (Hu et al., 2023) (Yasunaga et al., 2022) in the field of RALM have utilized these datasets."
  ]
}